<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.10.10">
<l>uṟuva tāva tettēvu mevvula kaṅkaḷu maṟṟuntaṉpāṉ</l>
<l>maṟuviṉ mūrttiyō ṭottit taṉaiyu niṉṟavaṇ ṇaniṟkavē</l>
<l>ceṟuvil cennel karumpo ṭōṅku tirukkuru kūrataṉuḷ</l>
<l>kuṟiya māṇuru vākiya nīḷkuṭak kūttaṉuk kāṭceyvatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Undertaking [that] is possible. While he stands in the manner that he stands as ever so much,</l>
<l>being equal with [his] flawless form, in any god, in all the worlds and in others,</l>
<l>acting as servants to the tall pot dancer who is the intended(?) glorious form</l>
<l>in Tirukkurukūr high with red paddy along with sugarcane in fields.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
